Whereas more than 2,000 members of the United States Armed
			 Forces have died in Afghanistan since 2001, more than 18,400 members have been
			 wounded, and thousands of members remain in harm’s way;

Whereas it is estimated that the United States has spent
			 more than $640 billion on aid and military operations in Afghanistan since
			 2001;

Whereas the United States has brought Osama Bin Laden to
			 justice, which was the original justification for removing the Taliban from
			 power in Afghanistan;
